```java
public static int rank(int key,int[] a){
 int lo=0;
 int hi=a.length-1;
 while(lo<=hi){
 int mid = lo+(hi-lo)/2;
 if(a[mid]>key) hi=mid-1;
 else if(a[mid]<key) lo=mid+1;
 else return mid;
 }
 return -1;
}
```

